Package: democracyData
Type: Package
Title: Access and Manipulate Most Available Democracy Datasets 
Version: 0.5.1
Description: Archives a large number of democracy datasets, many of historical 
    interest. It also provides a number of functions to download these datasets 
    (where available) and determine membership of a country in standard 
    membership lists of the state system (according to Gleditsch and Ward, 
    Correlates of War, or Polity).
